- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper proposes a lazy CEGAR algorithm for timed automata, which involves AI techniques.

- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is a possible category as the paper proposes an algorithm for improving the efficiency of reachability analysis in timed automata, which is a software engineering problem.
